BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: High Park Yoga
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/high-park-yoga/
UID:event_314111344@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260406T031128Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260507T200000
SUMMARY:High Park Yoga
DESCRIPTION:High Park Yoga\n**\\~Please [SIGN UP here](https://calendly.co
 m/breathinginnature/yoga-in-nature) for free before the class\\~**\n[Click
  here for a map of the exact location](https://goo.gl/maps/x1YMV41Bmhcf7ch
 b6).\n\nMy community classes in High Park are by donation\, for all bodies
 \, and no experience is required. What is yoga? We combine breath\, moveme
 nt and awareness\, all in the healing nature of High Park.\n\n**What to br
 ing?**\n\n* Yoga mat (optional - the grass is nice to yoga on)\n* Water\n*
  Weather-appropriate clothing/ blanket for relaxation\n\nWe yoga rain or s
 hine. There is shelter if we need it.\n\n[Exact location](https://maps.app
 .goo.gl/9424Zn5G1Xf4kTEj7)\, close the the High Park Forest School by the 
 North Gate (short walk from High Park Subway station\, Bloor and High Park
  intersection).\n\nMy classes are by donation\, or pay what you can. It's 
 also drop-in\, so feel free to just show up. Donations can be made at the 
 class in person\, via our [Breathing in Nature Gift Economy](https://www.b
 reathinginnature.com/gift-economy/) or e-transfer to nici@breathinginnatur
 e.com. On average folks donate between $5-$30 per class.\n\nPlease don't h
 esitate to contact me if you have any questions. 416.885.0583\n\nIf you ar
 e wondering who I am and what I do\, feel free to check out my my [website
 ](https://www.breathinginnature.com/)\, [Instagram](https://www.instagram.
 com/breathinginnature/)\, [Facebook](https://www.facebook.com/nicole.bohr)
  page\, [my bio](https://www.breathinginnature.com/about/)\, or [my Linked
 In](www.linkedin.com/in/nicoleczerwinski/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/high-park-yoga/events/314111344/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260403T205945Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260403T205945Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
